---
// Challenge Section - O Problema da Black Friday
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-bf-black mb-6">
          Na Black Friday, sua mensagem precisa se <span class="text-nexus-creative-dark">destacar</span>. E <span class="text-nexus-respect">converter</span>!
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-nexus-creative to-nexus-respect mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem Description -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          A Black Friday é o maior pico de vendas do ano. Mas, em meio a tanto barulho e concorrência, como garantir que suas ofertas não apenas <strong>cheguem ao seu cliente</strong>, mas o levem à compra <strong class="text-nexus-creative-dark">NA HORA</strong>?
        </p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          O segredo não está em mais marketing, mas em marketing <strong class="text-nexus-respect">DIRETO</strong>, pessoal e impactante.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats/Problem Visualization -->
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <!-- Stat 1 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center border border-gray-200">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-500 mb-2">~20%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Taxa de abertura de e-mails</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 2 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center border border-gray-200">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 8h10M7 12h4m1 8l-4-4H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-3l-4 4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-500 mb-2">~5%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Alcance orgânico em redes sociais</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 3 - The Solution Teaser -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-nexus-creative/10 to-nexus-respect/10 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center border-2 border-nexus-creative/30 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-bf-gold text-bf-black text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-lg">
            A SOLUÇÃO
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto text-nexus-creative-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-nexus-respect mb-2">98%+</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-nexus-tech">Taxa de abertura com RCS</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Insight -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-nexus-respect/5 to-nexus-creative/5 border-l-4 border-nexus-respect p-6 rounded-r-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-nexus-respect" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-nexus-tech mb-2">A verdade sobre a Black Friday:</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Seus clientes estão no celular. Suas ofertas precisam estar lá também. E não de qualquer forma - precisam ser <strong>visuais</strong>, <strong>interativas</strong> e <strong>irresistíveis</strong>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
